            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "建筑材料也很特殊呢。\\n这一带之所以成为禁区\\n难道是跟这栋建筑有关……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "这、这是什么声音！\\n是从里面传来的吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "该死，应该是发生了什么事……\\n看来我们只能进去\\n一探究竟了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "听好了艾德，\\n你千万不要离开我身边。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "嗯。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，我们走吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这里是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "搞什么……\\n净是些莫名其妙的东西……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "我也是第一次见……\\n和在香榭利亚见到的魔导兵器\\n是同一类东西吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "大家快来看！\\n这里写着什么字哦！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "唔，我看看……\\n呃，全是没见过的文字……\\n根本看不懂啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "这是！古阿尔贝里亚语……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝，你看得懂！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "嗯，我以前在教会学过一点……\\n这是早期伊利亚教的圣典里\\n使用的古代文字。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝，你真厉害！\\n那这上面写着什么呀？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我看看……\\n魔幻炉——采集口、调节阀……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "啥玩意儿？\\n都是些没听过的词啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "魔幻炉……\\n我有所耳闻。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "据说很久以前有一种通过吸收\\n自然界的魔力来人工炼成魔力的技术。\\n不过我也是第一次见到实物……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "库菈乌都是第一次见……\\n那就意味着，这已经是\\n很久很久以前的东西了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "也就是说，\\n这里是比旧狄涅尔帝国\\n更古老的太古文明遗迹吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "听说为了遵守女神伊莉雅\\n与圣域龙订立的盟约，\\n人工生成魔力的技术都被废止了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "这么说，这也是那种技术的\\n产物之一吗。原来如此。\\n不过，要在这种地方做什么呢……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊，艾德！\\n不能随便乱走！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "哥哥……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "别担心，\\n我们会陪你一起找哥哥的。\\n好了，快过来这边……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "尤蒂尔——\\n阿尔贝里亚王室中\\n徒有虚名的王子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "你马上就会，坏掉的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120031_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n离那个孩子远点。\\n刚才的魔兽，是你搞的鬼吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "埃尔菲莉丝，\\n这话是什么意思！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我早就觉得他不对劲了。\\n老成的语气和态度完全不像个小孩。\\n你这家伙，究竟是什么人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "什么！这股力量是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "那团漆黑的瘴气……\\n是黑暗魔力！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不会吧……那家伙\\n为什么会有黑暗魔力啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "艾德，你究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我就说怎么如此热闹，\\n原来宾客已经到场了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾德",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "法尔艾斯哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，\\n真亏你能找到这里啊。噢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "贝维特，原来你在那里啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "贝维特！？\\n怎么回事……\\n你不是叫艾德吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "贝维特，\\n尤蒂尔怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "嗯，他是个幸福的王子呢，\\n对自己深信不疑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "你这讽刺的语气是什么意思！\\n相信自己有问题吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "艾德……法尔艾斯哥哥，\\n你认识这孩子吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你应该也有所耳闻吧。\\n至今行踪不明的\\n阿尔贝里亚王室第五王子……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶？第五……王子？\\n怎么突然说这个……\\n难、难道！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "没错……第五王子，名叫贝维特。\\n他也是我们这些继承了\\n龙之血的兄弟姐妹中的一员。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01",
                "100002_01",
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贝维特",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "艾德……是我的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "是尤蒂尔的哥哥！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "怎、怎么可能嘛！\\n他只是个小孩子啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这个世界可没有那么单纯，\\n双眼所见的事物\\n不一定是真相哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哼，你这家伙，\\n别耍我们了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我只是在陈述事实而已。\\n至于你们信不信，\\n就与我无关了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "贝维特……\\n你真的，是我哥哥吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "父王和莱昂尼多哥哥都说\\n第五王子行踪不明……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_13_06_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
